# Test: Color recommendation
Output docs/images/test-colors.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set TypingSpeed 30ms
Set Padding 20

Type "jdai --new"
Enter
Sleep 5s

Type "Recommend two contrasting color hex codes for a terminal UI"
Enter
Sleep 12s

Screenshot docs/images/test-colors.png
Sleep 2s
